column1: # data from Adaptive Charging Network API
# where timeseries charging power is not available assumed constant charge rate
# covid and charigng station initial startup period removed
# holidays near-holidays and brief charging interruptions removed with weekday persistence
# see acn-jpl-cleaning.py (also 2018-12-21; 2019-12-06; and 2020-01-03 are repalced with 1week persistence)
# Load (kW not scaled) is average over interval
# Persist (kW) is 1 working day persistence except fridays which is 14 days since there seems to be a biweekly reduction in load on fridays (see data/build JPL persistence.ipynb)
